&gt; Another option here would be to send a 201 (Created) or 204 (No  
&gt; Content) with a Content-Location pointing to the new resource and no  
&gt; response body; this way the server can indicate success without  
&gt; sending a response body the client won&#39;t be able to handle. The  
&gt; client can go do content negotiation with the new resource itself in  
&gt; the usual way if desired.
